<plot>After Bill, a wild man known as the Son-of-a-Gun, disrupts May's party, he is kicked out of town and told he will be shot if he returns. In the next County he finds May's young brother being cheated at poker. Recovering the money the boy lost, he brings him home. But before the boy can explain, his father shoots Bill.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?591939</url></doc>
